data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET. This  well maintained duplex.  Duplex has 2 units, 1st floor has 1 bedroom/1 bathroom. 2nd floor has 1bedroom/1bath. Has the potential to be used as a 2 bedroom.  Great investment opportunity! This duplex also features a completely finished studio space in the basement with rear access and driveway. This duplex could be perfect for an owner occupant or an investor who just wants to add to their portfolio. Seller has relocated out of state due to family member illness.  Don't let this opportunity pass you by. Seller will also give buyer a 1 year Home Warranty. Seller may also be open to giving some assist.  Schedule your appointment today!
